headline: PNC Bank Agrees to Acquire Aqueduct Capital Group to Complement Harris Williams Capabilities
summary: PNC Bank today announced entry into a definitive agreement to acquire Aqueduct Capital Group, a placement agent focused on raising capital for private equity, private credit and real asset managers through its broad access to sophisticated, global pools of capital.
